My visual data story of instagram advertising

I want to know if the instagram ads I see are getting better over time so I added a line graph showing the change of Relevancy as I see more and more ads.

Additionaly, I wanted to know which category I see more often. I find it interesting to see if instagram will show more ads based on my interest, for example I like cooking and eating out food. Could this mean I see more food ads? Lets have a look!

Expanding on the previous graph, I made a plot to see which categories I like the most.

Finally, a bar graph showing what hour of the day I see the most ads in. This graph shows that I see the most ads at 11am.
